{
  "title": "Miceller",
  "publicationStatus": "public",
  "labEnvironment": "production",
  "subtitle": "Utforsk den potensielle energien til molekyl i olje og vatn.",
  "category": "",
  "subCategory": "",
  "screenshot": "",
  "aspectRatio": 1.1,
  "fontScale": 1,
  "lang": "nn-NO",
  "i18nMetadata": "",
  "credits": "",
  "helpOnLoad": false,
  "aboutOnLoad": true,
  "about": [
    "Vel om molekyla skal vera i olje eller vatn og observer korleis dei blir påverka av ",
    "omgivnadene og dei andre molekyla. Desse molekyla har hydrofile (polare) og hydrofobe ",
    "(ikke-polare) delar. Desse blir påverka ulikt av omgivnadene dei er i. Legg merke til korleis ",
    "den potensielle energien endrar seg når molekyla går saman i miceller.",
    "***",
    "*This simulation was developed by [the Interactions project](https://concord.org/projects/interactions \"the Interactions Project\") ",
    "with funding from the National Science Foundation (DRL-1232388) in partnership with ",
    "[the CREATE for STEM Institute](http://create4stem.msu.edu/ \"the CREATE for STEM Institute\") at Michigan State University. To learn more, ",
    "[visit the Interactions curriculum collection](https://learn.concord.org/interactions \"visit the Interactions curriculum collection\") in ",
    "which this simulation is embedded.*"
  ],
  "theme": "",
  "showTopBar": true,
  "showBottomBar": true,
  "padding": 10,
  "models": [
    {
      "type": "md2d",
      "id": "salt",
      "url": "models/lab-version/1/md2d/interactions/micelles/model.json",
      "onLoad": [
        "onStart(function() {",
        "  setComponentDisabled('drag', true);",
        "});",
        "onStop(function() {",
        "  setComponentDisabled('drag', false);",
        "});"
      ],
      "viewOptions": {
        "controlButtons": "play_reset",
        "controlButtonStyle": "text"
      }
    }
  ],
  "propertiesToRetain": [],
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "solvent",
      "initialValue": "water",
      "onChange": [
        "if (value === 'water') {",
        "  set('backgroundColor', '#A2E0F9');",
        "  setTextBoxProperties(0, {text: 'Vatn'})",
        "  setAtomProperties(3, {charge: 20})",
        "} else if (value === 'oil') {",
        "  set('backgroundColor', '#FFE200');",
        "  setTextBoxProperties(0, {text: 'Olje'})",
        "  setAtomProperties(3, {charge: -20})",
        "}"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "outputs": [],
  "filteredOutputs": [],
  "helpTips": [],
  "dataSets": [],
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "pe-graph",
      "type": "barGraph",
      "property": "potentialEnergy",
      "min": -150,
      "max": 40,
      "title": "Potensiell energi",
      "titleOn": "right",
      "labels": 0,
      "units": false,
      "gridLines": 10,
      "labelFormat": "0.1f",
      "barWidth": "2em",
      "height": "100%",
      "barColor": "#e23c34",
      "fillColor": "#fff",
      "tooltip": "",
      "helpIcon": false
    },
    {
      "id": "solvent",
      "type": "radio",
      "style": "radio",
      "orientation": "horizontal",
      "label": "Vel løysemiddel",
      "labelOn": "left",
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "Vatn (polar)",
          "value": "water"
        },
        {
          "text": "Olje (ikkje-polar)",
          "value": "oil"
        }
      ],
      "property": "solvent",
      "retainProperty": true,
      "disabled": false,
      "tooltip": "",
      "helpIcon": false
    },
    {
      "id": "drag",
      "type": "radio",
      "style": "radio",
      "orientation": "horizontal",
      "label": "Flytt/roter molekyl",
      "labelOn": "left",
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "Flytt molekyl",
          "value": "translate"
        },
        {
          "text": "Roter molekyl",
          "value": "rotate"
        }
      ],
      "property": "onAtomDrag",
      "retainProperty": true,
      "disabled": false,
      "tooltip": "",
      "helpIcon": false
    }
  ],
  "layout": {
    "right": [
      "pe-graph"
    ],
    "bottom": [
      [
        "solvent"
      ],
      [
        "drag"
      ]
    ]
  },
  "template": "simple"
}
